{
  "chapter": 42,
  "chapter_summary": "裴珏在冷谷双木与长虹剑、摄魂刀的激战中挺身而出，制止了战斗。冷谷双木以连环七掌逼退敌手，展现惊人实力。龙形八掌檀明唤出门下弟子苗豹参战，苗豹手持七节银鞭，神力惊人，将冷枯木逼得狼狈不堪。裴珏不顾安危闯入战圈，以海天秘笈绝招\"探囊取物\"两次擒住苗豹银鞭，最终断其兵器，令群豪震惊。檀明出面制止苗豹后，露出令裴珏心寒的微笑，使他忆起幼年在飞龙镖局的种种往事。檀明随即向冷谷双木发出公开挑战，声称赤手空拳便要取二人性命，生死对决一触即发。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "檀大叔，你说小侄的话，可有道理？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "江湖间事，非你能知，你年纪还轻，还该——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_miao_bao",
      "text": "豹子！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "豹子",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "豹子在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_miao_bao",
      "text": "你自觉可有把握？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "豹子",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "只能一人！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_miao_bao",
      "text": "叫少衍与罗义以二击一，你去应付一人，败了休来见我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_bian_shao_yan",
      "text": "少衍，闪过右边。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "豹子",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "这里来！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_miao_bao",
      "text": "无知野人，也要来动手么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "豹子",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "你说我是野人么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_miao_bao",
      "text": "正是！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你要做什么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_bian_shao_yan",
      "text": "两位赏我薄面，暂请住手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_miao_bao",
      "text": "豹兄——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "豹子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你也要来送死！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "豹子",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "开！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "豹子",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "开！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_miao_bao",
      "text": "豹子，住手！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_miao_bao",
      "text": "还不下去！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "人道雏凤之声，必定清于老凤，贤侄你一鸣惊人，檀大叔心里自然欢喜，但此刻你还是走开些得好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "贤昆仲绝技惊人，老夫看得也觉技痒，若是贤昆仲并不完全依仗着我那裴贤侄的话——",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "老夫谨向两位挑战！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说'龙形八掌'能在多少招之间击败冷家兄弟？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "五十招！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三十招！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我赌十五两，三十招！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我赌一匹川马，五十招！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "是比武抑或是——",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "无论是否比武，你兄弟两人只管一齐上来好了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "我檀明赤手空拳，若是不能取两位的性命，新仇旧恨，便从此一笔勾销，来，来，来！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    }
  ],
